      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/469904725_18473893498021204_8528857917103756498_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzUyMDExNDI0NDAzOTA5MDM5MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjYwMHg2MDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-HPILSocgR8Q7kNvwFl0-JQ&amp;_nc_oc=AdoICLt2ygRtx-XRpxWiffM_eeZPN0_8goO_MlbSoe7b3TZTO8iJ8nLXBpY9s7PkWvQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lHMxdhBOLnTkDKS6wkzAsA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy6Uv4GFdi7uv07ByJcx7Z1T4zEKJTqyZI5h-QfDCaTsQ&amp;oe=69C9FC64" alt="Instagram billede fra @amendunes" /></p><p><strong>@amendunes</strong></p><p>Death Jokes II @subpop<br/>
This is the last chapter of the final volume. Goodbye, I’ve barely said a word to you, but it’s always like that at parties - we never really see each other, we never say the things we should like to; in fact it’s the same everywhere in this life. Let’s hope that when we are dead things will be better arranged.</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/469904725_18473893498021204_8528857917103756498_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzUyMDExNDI0NDAzOTA5MDM5MA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjYwMHg2MDAuc2RyLkMzIn0%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=-HPILSocgR8Q7kNvwFl0-JQ&amp;_nc_oc=AdoICLt2ygRtx-XRpxWiffM_eeZPN0_8goO_MlbSoe7b3TZTO8iJ8nLXBpY9s7PkWvQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=lHMxdhBOLnTkDKS6wkzAsA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afy6Uv4GFdi7uv07ByJcx7Z1T4zEKJTqyZI5h-QfDCaTsQ&amp;oe=69C9FC64" alt="Instagram billede fra @amendunes" /></p><p><strong>@amendunes</strong></p><p>Death Jokes II @subpop<br/>
This is the last chapter of the final volume. Goodbye, I’ve barely said a word to you, but it’s always like that at parties - we never really see each other, we never say the things we should like to; in fact it’s the same everywhere in this life. Let’s hope that when we are dead things will be better arranged.</p>]]></content:encoded>
